{"tid":977381,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"石琪：《王者之後：重拳復仇》之美國精神","createTime":"2019-01-11T06:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T07:02:00.000Z","uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8928a375568749e4e9a1babe4faabb28f76c071a","tid":977381,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"自從1976年史泰龍自編自演第一部以來，《洛奇》就成為最長壽的荷里活拳擊片系列，簡直是「美國精神」的代表之一。四十多年來，其他西洋拳打擂台片很多，有些拍得更好，但都不及這系列賣座。<br />\n<br />\n《王者之後：重拳復仇 (Creed Ⅱ) 》是洛奇系列第八部，票房仍然不錯，成本五千萬美元，現已收入一億五千多萬美元，當然賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n現年七十三歲的史泰龍，不能上陣爭霸了，三年前在洛奇第七部《王者之後》轉任教練，訓練米高佐敦飾演的黑人拳師棘力 (Adonis Creed) ，爭奪重量級拳王寶座。今次劇情延續該片，史泰龍再做監製和師父，亦參與編劇。<br />\n<br />\n觀感怎樣呢？除了大捧黑人拳王之外，只是翻炒舊橋，宣揚「美國精神／大美國主義」，並無新意。全靠幾場打擂台保持刺激，至於英雄落難衰到貼地後重振雄風的公式，照例有通俗戲劇性。但不能期望精采，整體不過不失吧了。"},{"pid":"247fdec79eaaf9139e2367f32f5316b2a0e3ea32","tid":977381,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"復仇：《王者之後：神拳石琪》之美國精重"},{"pid":"009650e2f61eeab24f883af29f636ff0fb6eb287","tid":977381,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:20:53.000Z","msg":"復仇者石琪之重拳美國之神王精：後"},{"pid":"442fd0f1d7eb4e266fa2f23a83138eff91e206e6","tid":977381,"uid":118714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:25:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88d77c6b00004bec1fd635be191669664ac291c2","tid":977381,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T16:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a78aa7ca2ec21026198849329cc0a0333f0c29","tid":977381,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:10:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f636f21c42d10796aa01833c843d24f2d805401e","tid":977381,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:01:08.000Z","msg":"重拳石：琪後之王者復仇"},{"pid":"612725de3fa0272b6ad1da56ef625fc988508d35","tid":977381,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:02:06.000Z","msg":"重拳神精石：琪後之美國王者復仇"},{"pid":"8cff6064d9c85a51f81b7faf2df936e0e6b90b6b","tid":977381,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:38:21.000Z","msg":"《王者之石琪：後重拳復仇》"},{"pid":"0813b8b32bce3e0effad3a847444c7f8a6c5da1b","tid":977381,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:42:58.000Z","msg":"石琪：垃圾"},{"pid":"f6c78a8b7cbac1dbbeec821069b0997b61e03e05","tid":977381,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:48:16.000Z","msg":"石琪D 影評同連登仔有得fight ... 逢登必反"},{"pid":"20fbd8d6e4c427e0c8a8c7c9972cd520dbc99aba","tid":977381,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f6c78a8b7cbac1dbbeec821069b0997b61e03e05","tid":977381,"uid":171788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T01:48:16.000Z","msg":"石琪D 影評同連登仔有得fight ... 逢登必反"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:09:23.000Z","msg":"呢篇咁大段野，得最後幾句係評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a778fc75962a0910361a778134eafd09585a70","tid":977381,"uid":1903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T07:02:00.000Z","msg":"王者：《重拳之後：美國復仇》之石琪精神"}]}